          "reviewBody": "Environment:  Amethyst international school is best for academic and fee wise other than schools e.g vels. My kid is completed UKG in Amethyst and it was good environment and he improved his personal skills and done lot of activities over there.\n\nTeachers: Mainly well appreciate teachers, because what they handle and manage in crucial situations (e.g any functions) is wonder. And i would like thanks to Ramya mam who teaches UKG students and care of each one.\n\nPrinciple/management :  Managing any academy is not at all easy job , but amethyst is proved and successfully implemented.\n\nThanks.",
          "publisher": {
