            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "\"I am incredibly pleased with the education of my child receives at Amethyst (AIS)\nThe teachers are dedicated, caring, and go above and beyond to ensure each student's interest are fulfilled. The school fosters a nurturing environment that encourages growth, curiosity, academic & extra circular achievement.\n\nI'm confident that my child is in the best hands at (AIS), and I highly recommend it to other parents seeking an exceptional educational experience for their children.\"",
          "publisher": {
