          "reviewBody": "Excellent school. My daughter is completing LKG here this month. The effort taken by the staff to care for the children, make them feel at home and provide the best possible learning experience is really commendable. Qualified & highly motivated staff, good teaching & evaluation methods, reasonable fees, clear and timely communication to parents etc. are some of the other positives. Would highly recommend.",
